---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Learn about Erick Prospero, founder and CEO of Ninja Tropic eLearning, award-winning leader in AI-driven learning innovation and scalable content production."
>

  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="bg-navy text-white py-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-gold text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">About</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold">Erick Prospero</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bio Section -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-start">

        <!-- Headshot -->
        <div class="md:col-span-4">
          <img
            src="https://placehold.co/400x500/0f1f3d/ffffff?text=Erick+Prospero"
            alt="Erick Prospero, founder and CEO of Ninja Tropic eLearning"
            width="400"
            height="500"
            class="w-full rounded-sm shadow-lg"
          />
        </div>

        <!-- Bio Text -->
        <div class="md:col-span-8">
          <p class="text-gold text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">Biography</p>

          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-5 text-charcoal/85 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              Erick Prospero is an award-winning leader in AI-driven learning innovation, digital education strategy, and scalable content production for modern organizations. As the founder and CEO of Ninja Tropic eLearning, Prospero has built a reputation for helping associations, nonprofits, healthcare organizations, technology companies, and enterprise brands transform education into a measurable business asset through high-impact learning experiences, monetized training ecosystems, and AI-enhanced content operations.
            </p>
            <p>
              Known for blending instructional design expertise with emerging AI workflows, Prospero specializes in leveraging artificial intelligence to modernize how educational content is produced, personalized, and delivered at scale. His work focuses on helping organizations move beyond static eLearning models by creating dynamic, media-rich learning experiences that improve learner engagement while dramatically increasing production efficiency. Through the strategic use of AI-assisted content development, adaptive learning methodologies, automation pipelines, and modern instructional systems, he has become a leading voice in the future of educational content production.
            </p>
            <p>
              Over the past decade, Prospero and his teams have consistently earned recognition from some of the learning industry's most respected organizations, winning annual awards from Brandon Hall Group, eLearning Industry, and other major industry institutions for excellence in learning strategy, instructional design, digital education experiences, and innovative training solutions.
            </p>
            <p>
              A major focus of Prospero's work is helping organizations build educational content as a product rather than simply as internal training. He is widely recognized for helping associations, membership organizations, and learning brands turn educational programs into sustainable revenue engines by developing monetized learning ecosystems that increase member value, expand audience reach, and create recurring income opportunities.
            </p>
            <p>
              In addition to his consulting and production work, Prospero is a frequent speaker, podcast host, and industry contributor who regularly discusses the intersection of AI, instructional design, content strategy, and the future of digital learning. He is particularly known for humanizing conversations around artificial intelligence by positioning AI not as a replacement for educators and creators, but as a force multiplier that enables more meaningful, personalized, and effective learning experiences.
            </p>
            <p>
              Prospero is currently authoring a forthcoming book focused on AI-powered educational content production and the business strategy behind building profitable learning products.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Credential Stats Strip -->
  <section class="bg-navy text-white py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">

        <div>
          <p class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gold mb-2">10+</p>
          <p class="text-white/70 text-sm leading-snug">Years in the Industry</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <p class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gold mb-2">4</p>
          <p class="text-white/70 text-sm leading-snug">Brandon Hall Excellence Awards (2025)</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <p class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gold mb-2">Top 10</p>
          <p class="text-white/70 text-sm leading-snug">eLearning Industry Agency (3 Categories)</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <p class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gold mb-2">100s</p>
          <p class="text-white/70 text-sm leading-snug">of Learning Experiences Produced</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20 px-6 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-5">Bring Erick to Your Event</h2>
      <p class="text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Erick speaks at association conferences, enterprise learning summits, and industry events. Reach out to discuss availability and topics.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-gold text-navy font-semibold text-sm rounded hover:bg-gold-dark transition-colors"
      >
        Get in Touch
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
